    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Decorative ornaments worn on the breast; includes those sewn or pinned onto garments as well as those suspended by cords, beads, or the like, from the neck.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
